{"tid":1924711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高價賣爛菜惹民怨 孝感應城一小區聚集抗議","createTime":"2020-03-13T23:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T17:04:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac51c51b16bbcc7456475e7c82f688a2b2b5c2d0","tid":1924711,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T23:44:34.000Z","msg":"高價賣爛菜惹民怨 孝感應城一小區聚集抗議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4411342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5603%2F4411342&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=553023cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4411342</a><br />\n<br />\n湖北孝感應城海山小區昨晚爆發大批居民聚集籃球場的抗議事件，民眾長期不滿務業與賣場勾結賣高價值差的菜品，昨日一名聯繫組織購買平價菜的志願者被警方逮捕後，民怨四起，大批民眾聚集抗議，並大喊要社區書記「下課」、警察放人。<br />\n<br />\n受新冠肺炎影響，湖北實施封閉管理。小區居民日常所需物資全是由物業與業委會統一訂購到小區。但是高菜價、賣爛菜等問題時有所聞，大陸副總理孫春蘭在考察武漢市青山區翠園社區開元公館小區時，居民高喊<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「假的，全是假的、吃的都是高價菜。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">昨日應城發生的聚眾抗議事件，據當地民眾在網路上揭露，起因為統一配送的菜品貴、菜價差，有小區業主看不下去弄了些菜，按成本價出售，可能是觸及到他人利益，不准他賣，出言威嚇。昨日下午六點半，警察便將這名小區業主帶走，引起民怨。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n孝感市人民政府昨日發出說明，指出昨日晚間7點30約有100多人集在小區籃球場，防疫期間社區物資統一配送，嚴禁他人私售生活物品。一名程姓業主以愛心菜名義賣菜，被小區務業阻止並報警逮捕，導致「小區居民圍觀」。事發後，相關領導到現場，人員即散去。<br />\n<br />\n當日晚間8時半，應城市召開常委會議，對相關問題再次安排布署，防止類似事件發生。"},{"pid":"b039955b4c68d535f41a6c224fc6645148ea07fb","tid":1924711,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c408215c975d13eec8ffde5455ae1c4096d267cf","tid":1924711,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"沒有高價菜 哪有新中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d067a245b4705159e8c908e3397e635cff275a61","tid":1924711,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7614018efc32c0b32f2951d859f520c1717a76","tid":1924711,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce0acfccbdf8d21c5b3a0290e93dec43c669a46","tid":1924711,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"班支那人唔係成日話有得食就得㗎咩 咁撚多要求畀埋雜種個位你坐好冇呀"},{"pid":"6f03230cad850518a2c39d3badda6dde31710ccc","tid":1924711,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"又係發達時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}